  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Customer Service Representative",
  "description": "<p><ul><li>Manage Customer production order releases inclusive weekend support if require</li><li>Drive Customer Service Index to improve operational indices for customers.</li><li>Purchase Order Management. Acknowledge purchase orders within 24 hours, maintain/cancel redundant purchase orders and ensure correct shipping address. </li><li>Ensure there is always an active purchase order with pricing in SAP setup by Account Manager.</li><li>Assist Account Manager with customer’s material liability (EXOB – Excess and Obsolescence) to minimize STATS ChipPAC revenue exposure.</li><li>Analyze WIP projection daily & highlight any potential issues in missing daily shipment commit with actively alerted   customer & handle customer request/complaints in a timely manner, actively and reasonably resolve them, control the deterioration of the situation, improve customer satisfaction.</li><li>Meet or exceed forecasted revenue. Ensure production and service billings and invoiced promptly with minimal debit / credit notes.</li><li>Handle with Shipping on inbound/outbound requests.</li><li>Make arrangements for customer visits and maintain good relationships with customer<br /></li></ul><p><strong>Required Experience and Qualifications</strong> (Required knowledge, skills and experience---however acquired):</p><ul><li><p>Diploma and/or Degree graduate in any discipline.</p></li><li><p>Possess good interpersonal and communication skills.</p></li><li><p>Possess problem solving capability.</p></li></ul></p>",
