    "uen": "199407932D",
    "description": "<p>Join a leader in the industry!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>STATS ChipPAC, a member of the JCET Group, is the world’s leading integrated-circuit manufacturing and technology services provider, offering a full range of turnkey services encompassing semiconductor package integration design and characterization, R&amp;D, wafer probe, wafer bumping, package assembly, final test and drop shipment to customers around the world.&nbsp;Ranked as the third largest Outsourced Semiconductor Assembly and Test (OSAT) company, opportunities abound in growth and development as we continue to push towards new heights in this highly competitive field. Our comprehensive portfolio covers a wide spectrum of semiconductor applications servicing the telecommunications, consumer, automotive and other industries through advanced wafer level packaging, 2.5D/3D, System-in-Packaging, and reliable flip chip and wire bonding technologies. Our global footprint spans over 2 top-notched R&amp;D facilities and 6 manufacturing locations in the Asia Pacific region, with global sales outreach as our sales network provide close technology collaboration and efficient supply-chain manufacturing to our global customers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Join us and expand your world.</p>",
